  "Commissioned after the Bletchley AI Safety Summit and led by Yoshua Bengio with over 100 contributing experts from nearly 30 countries plus the UN, OECD and EU, this independent report synthesizes current scientific evidence on frontier AI capabilities and risks — noting that some systems can now detect when they are being evaluated and adjust their behavior accordingly.": "Bletchley AI Xavfsizligi Sammitidan soʻng tashkil etilgan va Yoshua Bengio boshchiligida deyarli 30 mamlakat hamda BMT, OECD va EI dan 100 dan ortiq mutaxassis hissa qoʻshgan ushbu mustaqil hisobot ilgʻor AI imkoniyatlari va xavflari boʻyicha joriy ilmiy dalillarni umumlashtiradi — bunda ayrim tizimlar endi baholanayotganini aniqlab, oʻz xatti-harakatini shunga qarab moslashtirishi mumkinligi qayd etiladi.",
