  "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI": "DeepMind CEO calls for an independent standards body to regulate frontier AI",
  "Demis Hassabis proposed a FINRA-style regulator for frontier model releases: labs would submit models for review up to 30 days before deployment, voluntary at first, with a path toward mandatory compliance in the US market.": "Demis Hassabis ilgʻor modellarni chiqarish uchun FINRA uslubidagi tartibga soluvchi organni taklif qildi: laboratoriyalar joylashtirishdan oldin 30 kungacha modellarni koʻrib chiqish uchun taqdim etishi kerak boʻladi, dastlab ixtiyoriy tartibda, keyinchalik esa AQSh bozorida majburiy muvofiqlik sari yoʻl tutiladi.",
  "Denied": "Rad etilgan",
  "Deployable policy starter template": "Joylashtirish uchun tayyor siyosat andozasi",
  "Deployable policy starter template at /downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip — a minimal static site with the full machine-readable layer, ready for Cloudflare Pages or any static host.": "/downloads/agiright-policy-starter.zip manzilida joylashtirishga tayyor siyosat andozasi — Cloudflare Pages yoki istalgan statik hosting uchun tayyor, toʻliq mashinada oʻqiladigan qatlamga ega minimal statik sayt.",
  "Deploying machine-readable policies on your site": "Saytingizda mashinada oʻqiladigan siyosatlarni joylashtirish",
  "Disclaimer": "Mas'uliyatni cheklash bayonoti",
  "Distinct from human UI, SEO, or plain APIs, the AI Ingestion & Capability Layer gives websites a machine-facing architecture: a Manifest Layer (entry points like /llms.txt and /ai/manifest.json), a Corpus Layer (machine-readable knowledge), a Capability Layer (agent-callable tools), and a Governance Layer (provenance, licensing, versioning). Static-first, upgradeable toward APIs and MCP. Note: in this paper AICL names the ingestion architecture; on this site's protocol pages AICL refers to the AI Content Licensing Layer.": "Inson uchun moʻljallangan UI, SEO yoki oddiy API'lardan farqli oʻlaroq, AI Ingestion & Capability Layer veb-saytlarga mashinaga qaratilgan arxitekturani beradi: Manifest Qatlami (/llms.txt va /ai/manifest.json kabi kirish nuqtalari), Korpus Qatlami (mashinada oʻqiladigan bilim), Imkoniyat Qatlami (agent chaqira oladigan vositalar) va Boshqaruv Qatlami (kelib chiqish, litsenziyalash, versiyalash). Statikni birinchi oʻringa qoʻyadi, API va MCP tomon kengaytirilishi mumkin. Eslatma: ushbu maqolada AICL ingestion arxitekturasini nomlaydi; ushbu saytning protokol sahifalarida esa AICL AI Content Licensing Layer ni bildiradi.",
  "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm": "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm",
  "Docs": "Hujjatlar",
  "Docs / Examples": "Hujjatlar / Namunalar",
  "Document library": "Hujjatlar kutubxonasi",
  "Does AI have rights — and which framings are even coherent?": "AI huquqlarga egami — va qaysi yondashuvlar umuman mantiqiy?",
  "Download": "Yuklab olish",
  "Draft status": "Qoralama holati",
  "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026": "EU AI Act: What Actually Applies on 2 August 2026",
  "Educational demo: HMAC-SHA256 with a shared secret, showing request-bound, expiring, verifiable license tokens. Production tokens should be signed asymmetrically, with the publisher’s public key discoverable under /.well-known/.": "Taʼlimiy namoyish: umumiy sirli kalit bilan HMAC-SHA256, soʻrovga bogʻlangan, muddati tugaydigan, tekshirilishi mumkin boʻlgan litsenziya tokenlarini koʻrsatadi. Ishlab chiqarish tokenlari asimmetrik tarzda imzolanishi kerak, nashriyotchining ochiq kaliti esa /.well-known/ ostida topilishi kerak.",
  "Eight more /topics entries, this time researched by an AI agent rather than curated by hand — same rule as before: every source fetched and confirmed live, summaries an original paraphrase, before anything gets added. 14 entries total.": "/topics boʻlimiga yana sakkizta yozuv qoʻshildi, bu safar qoʻlda emas, balki AI agent tomonidan tadqiq qilindi — avvalgi qoida saqlanib qolgan: har bir manba jonli holda olinadi va tasdiqlanadi, xulosalar esa original qayta bayon boʻlib, shundan keyingina qoʻshiladi. Jami 14 ta yozuv.",
