  "Field names and semantics may change between draft versions.": "Maydon nomlari va maʼnolari qoralama versiyalari orasida oʻzgarishi mumkin.",
  "Fifteen languages live in total: English, Traditional Chinese, Simplified Chinese, Japanese, Korean, French, German, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Persian, Bengali, Hindi.": "Jami oʻn beshta til faol: ingliz, anʼanaviy xitoy, soddalashtirilgan xitoy, yapon, koreys, frantsuz, nemis, ispan, portugal, rus, arab, turk, fors, bengal, hind tillari.",
